Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀  劳你费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,还让你们特地跑过来  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不不  身体怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我是为了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊  老师  不要乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,只是内人夸张地把你们叫来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,只是住院检查而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,难得的机会好好休养吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  马上就要到完成的节骨眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不中用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,大渡海的进度怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就要进行装订了  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是么  那我就拭目以待了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,可是啊老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,突然住院还采集用例真是吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.06,0:06:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这已经是生活的一部分了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,受到您的教导真开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,因为有很多很感兴趣的词语嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,检查要花多长时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那个不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要住院多久也没有听说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:07:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但是老师的脸色也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不过还是让老师休息一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再回到工作上来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就像荒木先生说的  这可能是个好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,松本就是那样不会休息的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,大家  请不要介意继续专注于工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很期待大渡海的完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,要是有什么消息的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我会联络大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那就拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,请保重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好  那接下来就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,「か」行还剩下这么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的  会做完的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但好像还是有些晕头转向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么说  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,空气动力学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,空气冷却
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,无实物吉他弹奏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,计划落空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,空气质量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:08:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,空气净化器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,空气调节
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,空气传染
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,空御
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,寄居
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,空教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,气动扬水筒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,偶吟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,呼噜呼噜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:55.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,慰问品来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大家快来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,佐佐木小姐也快来吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了  头昏脑胀的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,稍稍休息一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\bord3\shad0\c&H030304&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1006,90)}目标！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\bord3\c&H030304&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1168,610)}工作的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\bord3\c&H030304&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1094,658)}如果有不明白的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\bord3\c&H030304&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1000,710)}马上向荒木岸边或者佐佐木确认
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,委托了要洗衣服的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,按顺序过来取
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.34,0:11:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你们怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,速度明显提高了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,大家效率都变好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我也工作明显变快了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:11:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那就原谅你做冒牌的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,马缔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,世界正在  词语正在消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.84,0:12:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,马缔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.74,0:13:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,马缔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,大家可能都到界限了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,有的人一直都没怎么回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去效率会下降的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,今天所有人都回家  好好休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:34.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  阿虎早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好久没吃到香具矢做的饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你有在好好吃饭么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:14:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不好好吃的话  就不给你拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.64,0:15:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我会好好品尝的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我去探望松本老师了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯　似乎周末能出院了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,老师的情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然能看见笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但时不时又会露出疲惫之色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,老师的年纪到底有多大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,单看感觉这14年来没有多大变化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯　的确是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果说已经是90以上的高寿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,或者说才68岁　都不会觉得奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,将毕生心血奉献给一样事物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是不通世俗的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,小光也是这样呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,时光流逝　却没有什么变化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,香具矢自我们认识以来　也没有变化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样　马缔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.84,0:16:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为设计非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那么这就让各岗位开始工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.14,0:16:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,呀　就知道马缔先生会喜欢这个设计
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯　这个设计很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,太好…　还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这边也没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这样所有的核对工作都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.84,0:17:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,终于*n
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你　努力了这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,（谢谢）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,马缔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦您啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,您…您也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,最开始觉得这件事太平凡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到却很享受关于辞典的这份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有什么事请再联系我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了*n　谢谢*n
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我先走了　留下来的大家加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真是有幸遇到这么好的团队
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,还没有结束哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦啦　回家路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.54,0:18:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好的　谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀　从打工的小哥那里听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,已经没有其他疏漏了不是么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,可喜可贺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这正是让大家热血沸腾的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,西冈你想干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,最近不怎么见得到你的踪影  现在有何贵干
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,等…　荒木先生好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我也在以自己的方式为了《大渡海》拚命工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,至于证据
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,锵锵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,《大渡海》的吉祥物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,其名为小海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！　哇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样　可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是的　超可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,（哇　好可爱）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,对于西冈来说　这个审美就不错了
